<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="the-other-day">the other day</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>前几天；前不久：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When I met him the other day, he had just come back from work, looking excited. 
前几天我碰到他的时候，他正好下班回来，看上去很兴奋。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 3</footer></div></div>